  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, multi-center study to evaluate the
      efficacy and safety of E6007 once daily for 8 weeks in Japanese participants with moderate
      active ulcerative colitis. Participants will be stratified by prior therapeutic treatment and
      Mayo score at Baseline, and will be randomized 1:1:1 to receive E6007 30 milligrams (mg),
      E6007 60 mg or placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
